(271, 9, 24, 'The Coral Island', 'the-coral-island', 'The Coral Island', 'The Coral Island', 'R. M. Ballantyne', 'Suno Kahaniyan Productions', 'Adventure', '06:06:00', NULL, 0, '<p>&quot;The Coral Island&quot; by R. M. Ballantyne takes you on an exciting adventure to a tropical paradise. Join three young boys, Ralph, Jack, and Peterkin, as they find themselves stranded on a deserted island after a shipwreck. Together, they must learn to survive, face challenges, and explore the wonders of their new home. This classic tale of friendship, bravery, and discovery will transport you to a world of imagination and escapades, where the beauty of nature and the spirit of adventure intertwine. Get ready to embark on a thrilling journey that will ignite your sense of wonder and ignite your own island dreams.</p>', '6_95c133723443d02269d2fa0e935900e8.jpg', '6_95c133723443d02269d2fa0e935900e8.jpg', NULL, '2023-06-19 06:19:50', '2023-06-18 09:02:21', NULL, NULL),
