(275, 9, 24, 'The Voyages of Doctor Dolittle', 'the-voyages-of-doctor-dolittle', 'The Voyages of Doctor Dolittle', 'The Voyages of Doctor Dolittle', 'Hugh Lofting', 'Suno Kahaniyan Productions', 'Adventure', '04:32:00', NULL, 1, '<p>An exciting story about a kind-hearted doctor who can talk to animals. Join Doctor Dolittle and his animal friends as they embark on thrilling adventures to far-off lands. From saving endangered species to outsmarting pirates, this heartwarming tale celebrates the power of friendship, compassion, and the wonders of the animal kingdom. Get ready to dive into a world where animals can speak and where the bond between humans and creatures knows no bounds. Prepare for a delightful journey that will ignite your imagination and warm your heart.</p>', '10_bc0283fad69fb6011f341381960a977b.jpg', '10_bc0283fad69fb6011f341381960a977b.jpg', NULL, '2023-06-19 06:22:13', '2023-06-18 09:08:03', NULL, NULL),
